_sText: This map has a lot of interactive type things in it. Some things may be confusing to a new player to the map as it is not obvious of what to do. In the download zip I have included a text document with a list of these possibly confusing obstacles. The official test server for my maps is 8.9.4.112, for alpha testing come join us and you can help find bugs in new maps. SPECIAL THANKS TO CHIZBONE FOR THE NAV FILE. COULDN'T HAVE MADE THE MAP AS IT IS WITHOUT YA!
